neys aren't filtering waste as well as they should.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036844,0.073469,0.096369,0.11622,0.12198,0.11881,0.10913,0.091624,0.078413,0.066384,0.053892,0.036867],"unified_progress":[0.043027,0.073094,0.090891,0.10202,0.10756,0.1004,0.10115,0.092876,0.089755,0.076328,0.066344,0.056549]},{"section":9,"text":"And there are red blood cell casts in her urine.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020969,0.061891,0.096868,0.12967,0.14139,0.13479,0.1197,0.095309,0.07379,0.060439,0.042501,0.022682],"unified_progress":[0.033786,0.071321,0.093158,0.10738,0.11391,0.10768,0.10346,0.094298,0.095696,0.072943,0.058307,0.048057]},{"section":10,"text":"Those are a big clue because they usually mean there's inflammation in the glomeruli, which are part of the kidney's filtration system.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034989,0.063287,0.085068,0.10433,0.11291,0.11531,0.11178,0.099776,0.090779,0.082331,0.062513,0.036933],"unified_progress":[0.041004,0.066656,0.085994,0.09823,0.10354,0.11143,0.10408,0.096194,0.091007,0.079868,0.067177,0.054814]},{"section":11,"text":"Oh, and there's also protein in her urine, but it's not the usual type you'd see in nephrotic syndrome.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029565,0.058564,0.085392,0.10953,0.12013,0.12001,0.11347,0.10067,0.088883,0.080257,0.060008,0.03353],"unified_progress":[0.038985,0.068237,0.08669,0.098818,0.10548,0.10359,0.10165,0.096518,0.095454,0.08228,0.067756,0.054552]},{"section":12,"text":"It's more like microscopic hematuria and proteinuria, which fits with glomerulonephritis rather than nephrotic syndrome.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033524,0.050431,0.070045,0.088427,0.1001,0.1071,0.11016,0.10601,0.10292,0.10087,0.080541,0.049879],"unified_progress":[0.039535,0.060272,0.078962,0.091276,0.097589,0.10732,0.10219,0.098935,0.095774,0.088217,0.076214,0.06371]},{"section":13,"text":"So, putting all these pieces together - the recent sore throat, the kidney symptoms, and the specific lab findings - I'm thinking this looks like post-streptococcal glomerulonephritis.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.021706,0.041485,0.056441,0.068701,0.078001,0.085732,0.09242,0.095815,0.10211,0.11454,0.12818,0.11487],"unified_progress":[0.029923,0.051661,0.065354,0.077017,0.083663,0.093018,0.094279,0.097641,0.10013,0.10162,0.10368,0.10202]},{"section":14,"text":"That's when the immune system reacts to a strep infection by attacking the kidneys.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.021869,0.034716,0.049083,0.064621,0.079666,0.094437,0.1081,0.11388,0.12213,0.13394,0.10941,0.068145],"unified_progress":[0.028472,0.049747,0.069451,0.081566,0.090832,0.10216,0.10331,0.10492,0.10271,0.099505,0.088979,0.078349]},{"section":15,"text":"Yeah, that seems to fit.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.10195,0.082323,0.078071,0.072011,0.074626,0.078555,0.083055,0.093566,0.085689,0.059995,0.06465,0.12551],"unified_progress":[0.19134,0.071838,0.061569,0.063066,0.072412,0.073341,0.10713,0.084963,0.083355,0.067131,0.063169,0.060685]},{"section":16,"text":"The timing matches up too, since post-strep glomerulonephritis often shows up a couple of weeks after a throat infection.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038284,0.047372,0.056863,0.067485,0.075636,0.085913,0.09479,0.098305,0.1047,0.11532,0.11452,0.10082],"unified_progress":[0.043531,0.064835,0.054934,0.083406,0.091164,0.094435,0.099835,0.098781,0.097211,0.095948,0.089619,0.086301]},{"section":17,"text":"So, I feel pretty confident saying that's what's going on here.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.015805,0.026135,0.031902,0.038114,0.043194,0.048578,0.054366,0.058268,0.068993,0.095669,0.20248,0.31649],"unified_progress":[0.012216,0.